window.bookSummaryJSON = "A day after unprotected sex with her boyfriend, a woman wakes up to find her pillowcase soaked in blood, the smell of old pennies drifting from her upper lip. After a week, the nosebleeds stop. Then it comes from her ears. And throat. And the doctors don't believe that she's bleeding at all. But what about the garbage can filled with bloody tissues? \"Haima\" is a short horror story that appears in M.J. Pack's collection <i>Certain Dark Things</i>, also available on Audible.com."; 
